<h2 id="section-top">Ear, Nose &amp; Throat</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1843">Lancashire Teaching Hospitals NHS Foundation Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">Main Switchboard<br/>01772 716565</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent16b372b502014af3adf5cba3349867e3">
</div>
<p>We provide comprehensive medical and surgical care for all ear, nose and throat and audiological conditions for children and adults.<br/><br/>Services are based at Ward 3, the ENT outpatient suite and operating theatres at the Royal Preston Hospital; and in the out-patients department at Chorley District General hospital.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.lancsteachinghospitals.nhs.uk/ear-nose-throat" target="_blank" title="Ear Nose and Throat">Click here to view more information on the Lancashire Teaching Hospitals website</a></p></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel name-serviceteamsummary">
